OL,3,CMan walks 30 miles up and down pier in
OL,4,Cmemory of his wife
OL,6,FA dedicated charity walker who
OL,7,Fsurvived open-heart surgery is taking
OL,8,Fon a 30-mile walking challenge around
OL,9,Fa pier to mark three decades of
OL,10,Ffundraising.
OL,12,FPaul Hobbs is walking 111 laps around
OL,13,FWeston-super-Mare's Grand Pier on
OL,14,FThursday 15 August to mark the
OL,15,Fanniversary.
OL,17,FOver the past 30 years, the 75-year-
OL,18,Fold has raised more than a million
OL,19,Fpounds for various charities, saying
OL,20,Fthat fundraising is "part of his life".
