OL,3,CMan walks 30 miles up and down pier in
OL,4,Cmemory of his wife
OL,6,FMr Hobbs is completing his latest
OL,7,Fchallenge in memory of his wife
OL,8,FMaureen, who died in June after being
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with terminal cancer.
OL,11,FHe is hoping to raise #10,000 for
OL,12,FCancer Research UK, to fund research
OL,13,Finto rare cancers that are untreatable
OL,14,Fand incurable.
OL,16,FAlthough he said he is feeling
OL,17,F"confident" about the walk, Mr Hobbs
OL,18,Fsaid he has to be careful as he
OL,19,Fsuffered a life-threatening aneurysm
OL,20,Fnear his heart in 2019.
